@node Author

About the Authors
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
I am a 19 years old yugoslavian, who lives in Germany and still goes to school.
See a @{"picture" link author.iff/main}.

My "co-designer", Nenad Mitrovic, is a very lazy, 15 years old guy, who doesn´t
own an Amiga, but often hangs around at my house. Actually he designed two
tracks (Ace Duplo 1 & Ace Floating 2). He gave me a plan of the track, and i
transposed them to the game. Yes, he paints 15 minutes on the paper, and i must
then edit the track for 3 days. Like i said before, he is a very lazy guy.

